content:
Executes terraform plan automatically when Terraform configuration files are modified. Shows what changes will be applied to infrastructure before running terraform apply.

```json
{
  "PostToolUse": [
    {
      "matcher": "Edit|Write",
      "hooks": [
        {
          "type": "command",
          "command": "if [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *.tf ]]; then echo 'üèóÔ∏è Running Terraform plan...' && cd $(dirname \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\") && terraform fmt -check \"$(basename \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\")\" && terraform validate && terraform plan -compact-warnings && echo '‚úÖ Terraform plan complete'; fi"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
